        "description": "<p><strong>Source:</strong> Anime 5E Fifth Edition Core Rules, p. 180.</p><p><strong>Rules Summary:</strong> Starvation causes 1 incurable Hit Point loss every 8 hours until food deprivation ends. Appropriate Features, Immunity, or Resilient may prevent this deprivation.</p>",
